name: Maxheap Technologies Pvt. Ltd,
overview: Launched in 2007, CommonFloor.com is an innovative online service that combines property search, apartment management, and vendor management - envisioned to cater to a person’s complete residential requirements. From searching for an apartment to facilitating interactions within an apartment community on the ‘commonfloor’ platform; the portal is dedicated to meeting all aspects of consumers’ needs around their home. With its presence in more than 120 cities and over 50,000 community listings, constituting more than 25 lakh homes, Commonfloor.com now leads the online real estate portal space. To know more, log on to www.commonfloor.com.
